274
00:22:29.074 --> 00:22:31.702
-Tchau.
-Até, Ham, amanhã às 8h.


275
00:22:31.743 --> 00:22:33.495
-Às 8h?
-Sim. Até.


276
00:22:33.537 --> 00:22:36.415
Tchau. Até amanhã.

277
00:22:37.374 --> 00:22:40.168
Benny, espere! Sua luva!

278
00:22:40.210 --> 00:22:41.920
Fique com ela, cara.

279
00:22:42.671 --> 00:22:44.798
Valeu!

280
00:22:46.216 --> 00:22:47.884
Espere, Smalls.

281
00:22:54.099 --> 00:22:56.893
